      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SAN SEBASTIAN (7) enjoys a class drop from the Nutrien Classic Sales series where he placed in a heat before finding the final too rich. This is much more suitable and he had had gone into that series off a win and a placing at Menangle. Draws wide but strikes at 50 per cent at this circuit and distance so looks well placed. WHITBYS DELIGHT NZ (6) led from one spot wider and fought well to win over this distance the last time she raced here three back. Leading hope. RUMOUR STRIDE (4) should be approaching peak fitness now and could enjoy the return to a circuit and distance where he is proven. NOTHING FINER (2) has been coming from wider or second row barriers so will enjoy this draw.",
